ut I feel like people are seeing what we are doing,\\\" Paris 2024 director-general Etienne Thobois said.\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1617, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.158014227630333e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1645, \"end\": 1660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9tienne_Thobois\", \"score\": 0.9999993218032185, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Etienne Thobois\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9tienne_Thobois\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9tienne_Thobois\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our concept\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"a large number\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"temporary sites\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1492}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1517}, {\"ngram\": \"constraints\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1561}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many central Metro stations will also be closed from July 18 until the day after the opening ceremony, which will see 6,000 to 7,000 athletes sail down the Seine on around 100 barges and river boats.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1824, \"end\": 1829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.211658162039436e-20, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many central Metro stations\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1695}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1725}, {