rea\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 45,000 officers will be on duty for the July 26 parade, assisted by thousands of soldiers and private security agents.\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Around 45,000 officers\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"duty\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"the July 26 parade\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2354}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2377}, {\"ngram\": \"soldiers\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2389}, {\"ngram\": \"private security agents\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On July 17, police in eastern France announced they had arrested a suspected far-right extremist who had made threats against the Games in a group on the Telegram phone application.\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2450, \"end\": 2456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999530986313919, \"rank\": 2.3539780100209374e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2574, \"end\": 2582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.829555233591844e-22, \"text\": \"Telegram\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2438}, {\"ngram\": \"a suspected far-right extremist\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"threats\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2555}, {\"ngram\": \"a group\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the installation of tens of thousands of metal security barriers along the opening ceremony route in Paris has outraged some residents, who feel closed in.\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2715, \"end\": 2720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.977492817216636e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the installation\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2630}, {\"ngram\": \"tens of thousands\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2651}, {\"ngram\": \"metal security barriers\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony route\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2711}, {\"ngram\": \"some residents\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a bit like being in Planet of the Apes,\\\" Aissa Yago, who lives on the Ile Saint-Louis in central Paris, told AFP this week from behind a barrier.\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2874, \"end\": 2879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.977492817216636e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2886, \"end\": 2889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999992654768872, \"rank\": 7.277292313223605e-07, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Planet\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2803}, {\"ngram\": \"the Apes\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2815}, {\"ngram\": \"Aissa Yago\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2828}, {\"ngram\": \"the Ile Saint-Louis\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"a barrier\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All they need to do is throw us some peanuts.\\\"\", \"from\"